summary: A CBBE conversion of nsk13s Wild Huntress Armor. BBP, TBBP and BodySlideable.
descriptionHtml:
[center][font=Tahoma]This mod converts [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53494/?]Wild Huntress Armor UNP[/url] by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/3373573/?]nsk13[/url].
For use with CBBE Bodies.

[img]http://static-1.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/61970-1-1422091020.png[/img]

[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/61970-0-1479866460.png[/img]
[size=5][/size][/font][font=Tahoma][font=Tahoma][size=2][b][size=4][font=Tahoma][size=2][size=2][size=4][b][color=#000000]×[/color][/b][/size][/size][/size][/font] Requirements [/size][/b][font=Tahoma][size=2][size=2][size=4][b][color=#000000]×[/color][/b][/size][/size][/size][/font][/size][/font][/font][size=2][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53494/?]

Wild Huntress UNP[/url]. [/size][font=Tahoma][size=2]Must be installed first. Override with my mod.[/size]
[size=2]- HDT Heels version requires [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36213/?]HDT HighHeels System[/url].[/size]
[font=Tahoma][size=2]- Caliente's [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]Beautiful Bodies Edition[/url] body meshes.[/size][/font]


[size=5][font=Tahoma][font=Tahoma][size=2][b][size=4][font=Tahoma][size=2][size=2][size=4][b][color=#000000]×[/color][/b][/size][/size][/size][/font] Acquisition [/size][/b][font=Tahoma][size=2][size=2][size=4][b][color=#000000]×[/color][/b][/size][/size][/size][/font][/size][/font][/font][/size]

The full set can be crafted at a tanning rack, under the leather category.


[size=5][/size][font=Tahoma][font=Tahoma][size=2][b][size=4][font=Tahoma][size=2][size=2][size=4][b][color=#000000]×[/color][/b][/size][/size][/size][/font] Credits [/size][/b][font=Tahoma][size=2][size=2][size=4][b][color=#000000]×[/color][/b][/size][/size][/size][/font][/size][/font][/font]

[font=Tahoma]Original UNP mod and all texture work belong to [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/3373573]nsk13[/url].[/font]

[size=2]Armor Mesh: by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20415/?]Brokefoots UNP Mashup Compilation by brokefoot[/url].
Boots Mesh: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/43381/?]Bobs Boots for CBBE and UNP HDT REQUIRED by Beazalbob69[/url][/size].

[font=Tahoma]Huge thanks to the entire team behind [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?]BodySlide 2 & Outfit Studio[/url] - without which this conversion would not have been possible.[/font]

[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/61970-0-1479866460.png[/img]
This mod is a Nexus exclusive! Please do not upload it anywhere else.
[/font][/center]
